------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A collection of utilities for an easier and smarter approach to openerp orm and xmlrpc resources
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

MODULES:

orm.py
------
Contains class OsvMixin, a mixin class for osv.osv objects which provides "shortcuts" methods to access data
in a quicker way.

rpc.py
------
Provides a Connection class to estabilish an xmlrpc session with the openerp server instance and a set of methods
to query, update and create objects.

